full_text: Case 1:19-cr-00830-AT Document 17 Filed 12/19/19 Page 15 of 15 15 JbpWnoeC Act until April 20, 2020. I find that the ends of justice served by excluding such time outweigh the interests of the public and the defendants in a speedy trial because this will allow time for the prosecution to produce discovery, for the defense to consider it, to decide whether to prepare motions, and for the parties to discuss a possible disposition. The defendants' bail status shall remain the same. The matter is adjourned. (Adjourned) SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300 DOJ-OGR-00021991
